subtitles: {"ar":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.986000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.505000000","text":"AUSSIE: أمامنا فريق Zayt على أرض مرتفعة، وصعد Khanada الآن."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.505000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.491000000","text":"صعد على العائق! إنه مسلح ببندقية الصيد التكتيكية الأسطورية."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.491000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:10.060000000","text":"Khanada يسقط Saf."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:10.060000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:13.213000000","text":"GUY: نفّذ 10 عمليات تصفية، ولا يزال في بداية المباراة، وحصد 178 نقطة."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:14.481000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:17.467000000","text":"SANCHOWEST: لكن هل تعجل بالقفز يا Shyo؟"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:17.467000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:18.651000000","text":"لا أصدق، أجل!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:19.035000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:22.288000000","text":"AUSSIE: إنهم أفضل اللاعبين، وأتوا جميعًا للعب."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:22.288000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:24.974000000","text":"هذه فرصتهم للاحتفاظ بالصدارة."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:24.974000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:27.961000000","text":"Commandment يخرج. يمكنه استخدام منصة الوثب لكنه لا يحتاج إليها."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:27.961000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.915000000","text":"بندقية صيد الشحن الكبيرة هذه تسببت في أضرار كثيرة هذا الأسبوع."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.915000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:36.069000000","text":"SUND0WN: والآن مواجهة ثنائية، هل سيصمد alithy وCriizux؟"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:36.069000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:38.288000000","text":"ينزل Criizux ليحاول حسم المباراة لصالحه."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:38.288000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:42.125000000","text":"ينجح Criizux في إسقاط اثنين ويضمن التأهل."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:42.125000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:45.111000000","text":"CHARLY: صار وضع Vadeal آمنًا ويحاول الحفاظ على مركزه المتصدر."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:45.111000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:46.613000000","text":"لديه 4 مشروبات درع صغيرة لكن هذا غير كاف."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:46.613000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:47.714000000","text":"لا يحتاج إلى العلاج."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:47.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:50.133000000","text":"يا لبراعته في التصويب! لقد نجح!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:52.736000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:57.424000000","text":"SUND0WN: سمعت عن الدُمى التي تُزين بها الرفوف لكن أمامنا الآن هؤلاء الرجال يعتلون رفًا."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:57.424000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:59.776000000","text":"وهم لا يتسمون باللطف كالدُمى."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:59.776000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:00.760000000","text":"...في الخارج هنا، ها هم أولاء!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:00.760000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:02.796000000","text":"في الحال! عثر على علامة 46، تجاوز الدرع."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:02.796000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:04.748000000","text":"تجاوز 54، تجاوز 72."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:04.748000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:08.084000000","text":"واحد. اثنان. ثلاث ضربات، لقد بذلت كل ما في وسعك!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:08.084000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:10.854000000","text":"CASTER: حاول الإطلاق، وحمى نفسه بسرعة،"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:10.854000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:13.056000000","text":"لقد اخترقوا الركن لمطاردة Pai."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:13.056000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:16.509000000","text":"هناك ثلاثة ملائكة تتعقب Pai."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:16.509000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:18.311000000","text":"يا إلهي، لقد أُصيب!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:18.311000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:21.047000000","text":"وها هو Ed!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:21.047000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:24.033000000","text":"ويخرج Blackoutz فجأة!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:24.033000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:26.886000000","text":"ZEKE: سيحصد الفائز جائزة مالية وشهرة ومجد.[جائزة إجمالية قيمتها 3000000 دولار]"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:26.886000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:28.855000000","text":"SANCHOWEST: يجب على Raqz و Traitor أن يقتلا Kami."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:28.855000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:30.740000000","text":"يصمد Kami ثم ينزل."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:30.740000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:32.525000000","text":"تجاوز علامتين!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:32.525000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:35.662000000","text":"CLAY: ليس لديه إلا نقطة صحة واحدة، ولا يمكن أن يتلقى ضررًا من المنطقة!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:35.662000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:38.648000000","text":"ويرتفع Poppins ثم يقفز هذه القفزة الرائعة."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:38.648000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:40.400000000","text":"AUSSIE: ملك الأرض المرتفعة Zayt، أيمكنه فعلها؟"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:40.400000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:42.502000000","text":"ستنخفض إلى ضرر واحد فعلًا!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:42.502000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:43.303000000","text":"MONSTERDFACE: أوه لا!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:43.303000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:46.289000000","text":"AUSSIE: سقط Zayt، وحقق Bucke الفوز."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:46.289000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:49.175000000","text":"كانت هذه نهاية مباراة رائعة في Fortnite."}],"de":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:02.986000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.505000000","text":"AUSSIE: Zayts Team von oben, Khanada baut gerade hoch."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:05.505000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.491000000","text":"Mit dem Sprungfeld nach oben! Er hat eine legendäre Schrotflinte."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:08.491000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:10.060000000","text":"Khanada elimniert Saf."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:10.060000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:13.213000000","text":"KOMMENTATOR:  Schon 10 Eliminierungen. Das Match hat erst angefangen und er hat schon 178 Punkte."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:14.481000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:17.467000000","text":"SANCHOWEST:  Aber kam der Schuss im Sprung zu früh?"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:17.467000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:18.651000000","text":"Nein, absolut perfekt!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:19.035000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:22.288000000","text":"AUSSIE: Das sind große Namen hier, und alle wollen den Sieg."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:22.288000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:24.974000000","text":"Das ist ihre Chance auf den ersten Platz."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:24.974000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:27.961000000","text":"Commandment geht raus, hat Abprallflächen, nutzt sie aber nicht."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:27.961000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.915000000","text":"Diese aufladbare Schrottflinte hat schon so viel Schaden gemacht."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.915000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:36.069000000","text":"SUND0WN: Und jetzt 2 gegen 2. Können alithy und Criizux bestehen?"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:36.069000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:38.288000000","text":"Criizux geht runter, um das Match zu entscheiden."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:38.288000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:42.125000000","text":"Er eliminiert beide und sichert sich so die Qualifikation."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:42.125000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:45.111000000","text":"CHARLY: Vadeal ist sicher da oben auf seiner Position."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:45.111000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:46.613000000","text":"Er hat vier kleine Schildtränke, das ist nicht viel."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:46.613000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:47.714000000","text":"Er kann sich nicht heilen."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:47.714000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:50.133000000","text":"Habt ihr diesen Schuss gesehen? Er gewinnt das Match!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:52.736000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:57.424000000","text":"SUND0WN: Man sagt, alles Gute kommt von oben. Diese drei kommen auch von oben."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:57.424000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:59.776000000","text":"Aber das ist nichts Gutes!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:59.776000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:00.760000000","text":"Los geht’s, hier der Angriff! Üzerine de 72 vurdu!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:04.697000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:08.136000000","text":"Bir, iki, üç atışla rakibini eliyor!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:08.161000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:10.854000000","text":"SUNUCU: Ateş etmeye çalışarak kendini korudu."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:10.854000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:12.920000000","text":"Pai'yi kovalamak için köşeyi döndüler."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:13.151000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:16.225000000","text":"Pai'yi resmen üç silahşörler kovalıyor."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:16.392000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:18.236000000","text":"İnanılır gibi değil, vurdu!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:18.291000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:21.022000000","text":"Ed düştü!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:21.047000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:23.754000000","text":"Blackoutz da düşüverdi!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:23.779000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:26.886000000","text":"ZEKE: İşin ucunda şan, şöhret, para, her şey var!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:26.886000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:28.855000000","text":"SANCHOWEST: Raqz ve Traitor, Kami'yi avlamalı."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:28.855000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:30.740000000","text":"Kami dayanmaya çalışıyor. Kami indi."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:30.740000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:32.446000000","text":"Sonunda birkaç mermi yiyor!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:32.492000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:35.757000000","text":"CLAY: Yalnızca 1 canı var.\nFırtına'ya bir an bile değme lüksü yok."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:35.782000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:38.491000000","text":"Poppins zıplayıp güzel bir görüş kazanıyor\nve rakibini vuruyor!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:38.516000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:40.574000000","text":"AUSSIE: Yükseklerin kralı Zayt başarabilecek mi?"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:40.599000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:42.502000000","text":"Her şey tek bir hasara bakıyor!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:42.502000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:46.216000000","text":"MONSTERDFACE: Olamaz!\nAUSSIE: Zayt düşüyor! Bucke kazanmayı başardı!"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:46.241000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:49.277000000","text":"Bir Fortnite maçından isteyeceğimiz her şeyi verdi!"}]}
